extra_descs.desc:
   This large machine makes a considerable noise as its unseen insides whir and
click continuously away.  The only noteworthy external parts are a large metal
tray that looks as though it opens and closes, releasing its contents to the
inner parts of the machine, also a large nozzle with a shelf placed
strategically beneath it.  A control board with three colored buttons is fixed
to the front of the machine.  The red button is inscribed with the word - press,
the blue button with switch, and green with turn.

